    schema1:description "The Rt Hon Esther McVey was Minister without Portfolio in the Cabinet Office between 13 November 2023 and 5 July 2024. She was previously the Minister of State at the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government from 24 July 2019 to 13 February 2020."@en ;
